Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:04.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  违背了诺言？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:09.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,面临危机时就要召唤我
